Falling in love with the gym again 🏋🏽 I’ve been to the gym on/off for years now but have never managed to give it 100% until these last two months. 6kg up already. Something about pushing your body to it’s limits & seeing progress is so rewarding. It’s a process, but I love it 🫡  Nowhere near where I wanna be, but It’s only just the beginning 😎 Let me know if you’re interested in seeing how I progress! 🖤

Bring on 2024, this is only the beginning.. 🏋🏽 Currently training 6 days a week with one rest day. Eating in a slight surplus and starting to put on some good size 💪🏼 Remember, a good pump, lighting and angles does wonders, I definitely don’t look like this just walking around lol. Maybe one day..
